data.description: Charming country cottage in Blue Ridge Shores with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Located on 2 lots,  with a detached garage/storage space for all your lawn equipment and tools.  This house backs up to woods for great privacy while you enjoy the scenery from your back deck.  Blue Ridge Shores is a quiet gated community tucked around Lake Louisa with 5 miles of shore line.  All homes have lake and beach access.  There are lots of things to do in the community, fishing, boating, walking trails, tennis courts, basketball courts, play grounds and a community center.  Come check it out!
